room_title: Escape room "Beasley's Billions" by Tick Tock Escape Room in Overland Park
review: My first escape room. We did Beasley's and had a really great time! Will definitely come back. Customer service was wonderful.

room_title: Escape room "Beasley's Billions" by Tick Tock Escape Room in Overland Park
review: Had so much fun solving puzzles for Bradley's Billions! We love that they had two rooms that are the same and we could compete against each other to see who finished first! Thank you Tick Tock Escape Games!!

room_title: Escape room "Beasley's Billions" by Tick Tock Escape Room in Overland Park
review: Loved the Beasley's Billions room! The puzzles were excellent and challenging plus they were relatable for everyone in the room! I highly recommend Tick Tock Escape games and will be back soon to do the Pyramid room!

room_title: Escape room "Beasley's Billions" by Tick Tock Escape Room in Overland Park
review: Our group of six had a great time! With two adults and 4 teens we were able to escape just in time (with great help from the staff). We did the Beasley's Billions room, and can't wait to come back and try the other!

room_title: Escape room "Beasley's Billions" by Tick Tock Escape Room in Overland Park
review: We have done several escape rooms throughout Kansas City and Beasley's billions was one of our faves. It was challenging but not over the top too challenging. We didn't escape but since we were close they let us finish! We love escape rooms and glad we tried this one out!
